https://mantledbeasts.carrd.co/
Va'ji
"The Spark" faction leader name

Apparel:
- Visor / Mantle: Made for Mantled Beasts, improves the hearing, sight, manipulation, and talking of Beasts who wear it, but has no effect on non-Beast pawns as they visor simply doesn't fit. (requires C# to check the pawn's genes on equip, and more C# to display the wearer's mood via changing masks). Can by dyed to change the mask's color. Should come in a few varieties: Normal (Aegiscite), Industrial (Components), Armored (Plasteel), Tribal (Woody), Archotech. Should be genetically sad if not wearing them. Should make some styles for Ideology.
- Mantlegear: Includes Chest Plate and Body Strips, comes in a few varieties that provide differing benefits and improves manipulation and moving to any pawn wearing them as they can generally be helpful for anyone. Applies a hediff to Beasts to display the tail strips. Varieties should include: Normal, Industrial, Laborer, Surgeon, Armored, Tribal, Archotech. Should be genetically sad if not wearing them.

Items:
- Va'ji mushrooms: can be purchased from either orbital goods traders or the Va'ji faction. When cooked with, provides a +6 mood bonus.
- Aegiscite: can be purchased from either orbital goods traders or the Va'ji faction. can act as metal, wood, and stone. Required component for crafting your own mantlegear and visor, after equivalent research is completed

Plants:
- Va'ji mushroom: Grown under highly specific conditions; must be grown underground near water. Once grown, will sometimes emit toxic gas which can quickly put those who are not protected to sleep before consuming them. Cannot be planted next to other Va'ji mushrooms

Genes:
(cosmetic)
- Va'ji fur (this should be the target for any genetic sadness from lacking apparel)
- Va'ji ears
- Va'ji tail
(utility)
- Va'ji paws (Custom, increased movement speed, hunter stealth, and melee damage) -4
- Heat super-tolerant -2
- Digitigrade (Alpha Genes) -1
- Larger (Alpha Genes) -1
- Strong intellectual -1
- Strong mining -1
- Low libido
- Slow gestation (Alpha Genes) +1
- Reduced fertility (Alpha Genes) +1
- Frail back (Alpha Genes) +1
- Delicate +3
- Poor eyesight (Custom, lowers Sight in both eyes to 0.35x while applying same accuracy debuffs as Nearsighted) +4
(compatibility)
- Canine genitalia (RJW Genes)
- Marine genitalia (RJW Genes) (doesn't exist :c )

